--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
This project utilizes the OpenSource AllJoyn to find the Server In the same NetWork Scope
the OpenSource Efflux is an OpenSource RTP video transmission libs.

The procedure is :
A. find the server ip
B. set up an RTP session
C. communicate by sending simple message
